                        <div class="content">
                            <h3>Take Control of Your Patients!</h3>
                            <p>
                                Our system is a registration and management tool used in healthcare services. It provides users with basic features such as recording, updating, deleting, and viewing patient information. Our system is a user-friendly solution aimed at improving healthcare services and meeting the needs of patients.
                            </p>
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <a href="#" class="more-btn">Learn More <i class="bx bx-chevron-right"></i></a>
